{"id": 3091, "genre": 1001, "title": "如果要列个「这一年，我都失去了什么」清单，你会填什么？", "description": "环顾自己的生活，你觉得哪些东西是在这一年之间消失的？（题图来自：iStock ©️ jossdim）", "record_count": 1809, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20191215150958AeI0Wg8Fy6HbhMZN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-12-15T17:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 350720, "content": "一事无成，晚上睡不着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1436141}, {"id": 350721, "content": "失去了学生时代的懵懂无知，越来越能体会到大人世界的辛酸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674782}, {"id": 350723, "content": "失去了对舍友的耐心", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1446404}, {"id": 351237, "content": "一年的时光", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675943}, {"id": 350727, "content": "失去了时光", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1175578}, {"id": 350728, "content": "失去了一点勇气，一点坚持和一点自我", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337149}, {"id": 350729, "content": "时间的失去\n耐心的失去\n学习能力的减弱\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1652167}, {"id": 350730, "content": "希望", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657728}, {"id": 350744, "content": "结婚、生了小孩，没有自己了～^_^", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473258}, {"id": 352281, "content": "一段学生时代的幼稚爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1679963}, {"id": 350749, "content": "失去最爱我的外婆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674809}, {"id": 351006, "content": "失去了探索向前的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675282}, {"id": 351011, "content": "失去了以前看番的快乐和阅读经典作品的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419123}, {"id": 351013, "content": "失去了一半的头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1675294}, {"id": 350758, "content": "静下心来读诗写诗的能力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674815}, {"id": 351271, "content": "Lose my mind", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1393132}, {"id": 351016, "content": "永远最爱我的父亲，以及我的31岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282756}, {"id": 350761, "content": "一起八年的她，我的另一半", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674817}, {"id": 350765, "content": "失去一个好基友，再得到一个。打平了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 615336}, {"id": 350767, "content": "失去放松的能力，努力找回中", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 217198}, {"id": 351023, "content": "失去了有趣的365天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1350348}, {"id": 350773, "content": "我失去了在11点半之前睡觉的习惯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369622}, {"id": 351542, "content": "失去了盲目乐观", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1666326}, {"id": 352310, "content": "好像没那么天真了\n少了一点笃定\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1579812}, {"id": 351035, "content": "一个亲人，几分动力，还有和朋友聚会的机会", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609324}, {"id": 350781, "content": "失去了一个人，失去了睡眠时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674608}, {"id": 350531, "content": "一整年的时间，感觉自己好像也没做啥就过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 255, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350788, "content": "失去了你，《好奇心日报》", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1341302}, {"id": 350533, "content": "刷社交媒体的动力，现在觉得不刷反而心情更好一点", "image": null, "praise_count": 270, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350789, "content": "真心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674840}, {"id": 350535, "content": "（一部分）友谊，工作之后跟一些以前的朋友感情渐渐淡了", "image": null, "praise_count": 177, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350791, "content": "期望", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665821}, {"id": 350537, "content": "耐心，现在看剧看文章都彻底变成两倍速了", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 350795, "content": "健康", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 972842}, {"id": 350796, "content": "热情，耐心，时间，信任感，自信，充足的睡眠，未成年热不的身份", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1549235}, {"id": 350797, "content": "时间和青春இдஇ (;´༎ຶД༎ຶ`)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1497481}, {"id": 351055, "content": "爱情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1573736}, {"id": 350803, "content": "快乐损失的最多，于是发现它是最重要的事情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1674865}, {"id": 350808, "content": "和善", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1311339}, {"id": 350810, "content": "19年末，又抑郁了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665340}, {"id": 350812, "content": "除了学习都不用操心的中学时代", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1419051}, {"id": 351324, "content": "精神以及身体的健康，大量的学业工作和超负荷的人际交往让人喘不过来气，总是把自己放在最后，太累了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1560500}, {"id": 350818, "content": "失去了单身的快乐，婚姻增强了我和另一半及其家人的粘性，但同时我失去了许多陪伴我的朋友、家人的乐趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 804958}, {"id": 352357, "content": "好奇心", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1681230}, {"id": 350824, "content": "胶原蛋白", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1528961}, {"id": 351083, "content": "失去了方向，感觉特别迷茫", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208912}, {"id": 350831, "content": "逐渐发觉自己没有底气和实力时候，失去了想去旅行的心情", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1637261}, {"id": 351087, "content": "头发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1558782}, {"id": 351089, "content": "失去了“自由身”，增加了一个“甜蜜的负担”，对，我居然生了一个人！！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 172446}, {"id": 350836, "content": "365天", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1665465}]}